          <title>Google Confirms Eclipsa Audio Support for Android in 2025 - AOSP Update Brings Spatial Audio Tech to the Largest Number of Devices</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Eclipsa Audio, a new spatial audio technology by Samsung and Google, is coming to Android Open Source Project (AOSP) release this year. This update will bring it to the largest number of devices, but lack of headphones support remains an issue.]]></description>
